<h1>Nyhedsgruppen dk.edb.internet.webdesign</h1><p>Gruppen er til spørgsmål/diskussion af de problemer der opstår ved fremstillingen af hjemmesider. Hovedvægten i gruppen lægges på debat af designløsninger og opbygning af websitet.</p><hr /><div class='newsbox'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_reply.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?mode=form&amp;ReplyID=%3C3c8752ec%241%40news%2Ecapgemini%2Ese%3E'>Svar på dette indlæg</a>&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_new.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?mode=form'>Skriv et nyt indlæg</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_list.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp'>dk.edb.internet.webdesign</a></div>

<!-- FreeFind End No Index -->

<ul class='messageheaderlist'><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Afsender:</span></strong> Claus&nbsp;Rasmussen&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='mailto:claus.rasmussen@capgemini.dk'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon.newsgroups.mail.gif' alt='claus.rasmussen@capgemini.dk' /></a></li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Organisation:</span></strong> Cap Gemini A/S</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Dato:</span></strong> 7. marts 2002 kl. 13:59</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Emne:</span></strong> <strong>Netscape 4.7 udfordring - &lt;table width&gt; problem!</strong></li></ul>

<p><span class='normal'>Hej NG </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Jeg har en 'lille' udfordring mht. Netscape 4.7 underst&#248;ttelse af tabeller! </span><br /><span class='normal'>Jeg har observeret at n&#229;r jeg har nedenst&#229;ende tabel, s&#229; bliver bredden af </span><br /><span class='normal'>tabellen i Netscape 4.7 st&#248;rre end de 366 px som angivet i table width. Som </span><br /><span class='normal'>jeg ser det, skyldes det at den f&#248;rste td med teksten 'Lang overskrift' g&#248;r </span><br /><span class='normal'>'et-eller-andet' s&#229;ledes at tabel-bredden bliver &#248;get - sandsynligvis </span><br /><span class='normal'>procent-vis, da jeg mener at Netscape 4.7 omregner pixel-angivelser til </span><br /><span class='normal'>procent. Men hvordan f&#229;r jeg defineret det s&#229;ledes at tabellen ALDRIG bliver </span><br /><span class='normal'>st&#248;rre end den bredde jeg angiver i tabel-bredden? </span><br /><span class='normal'>Det er rimeligt vigtigt for mig at f&#229; l&#248;st problemet, da der til venstre for </span><br /><span class='normal'>nedenst&#229;ende tabel er en lodret LIGE streg, som ellers bliver 'kn&#230;kket' hvis </span><br /><span class='normal'>tabel-bredden bliver &#248;get! </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>H&#229;ber at i kan hj&#230;lpe! </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>P&#229; forh&#229;nd tak </span><br /><span class='normal'>Claus Rasmussen </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>********************************************************** </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;table width=&quot;366&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'>    &lt;tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;366&quot; colspan=&quot;8&quot;>&lt;p </span><br /><span class='normal'>class=&quot;Headlines&quot;>Bla.bla.bla.bla&lt;/p>&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>    &lt;/tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>     &lt;tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;111&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Overskrift&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;42&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 1&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;42&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 2&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;42&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 3&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;42&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 4&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;41&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 5&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;41&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 6&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;5&quot;>&lt;img src=&quot;blank.gif&quot; width=&quot;1&quot; height=&quot;1&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; </span><br /><span class='normal'>alt=&quot;&quot;>&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>    &lt;/tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>    &lt;tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;111&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Lang overskrift&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;42&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 1&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;42&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 2&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;42&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 3&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;42&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 4&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;41&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 5&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;41&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>Tekst 6&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>        &lt;td width=&quot;5&quot;>&lt;img src=&quot;blank.gif&quot; width=&quot;1&quot; height=&quot;1&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; </span><br /><span class='normal'>alt=&quot;&quot;>&lt;/td> </span><br /><span class='normal'>    &lt;/tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/table> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'></span><br /></p><hr /><ul class='newslist'><li class='newslist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?messageid=%3C3c8752ec%241%40news%2Ecapgemini%2Ese%3E' title='Netscape 4.7 udfordring - &lt;table width&gt; prob...'>Netscape 4.7 udfordring - &lt;table width&gt; prob...</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(07-03-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;Claus&nbsp;Rasmussen)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?messageid=%3Ca67m8n%24ks0%241%40sunsite%2Edk%3E' title='Re: Netscape 4.7 udfordring - &lt;table width&gt; ...'>Re: Netscape 4.7 udfordring - &lt;table width&gt; ...</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(07-03-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;scn)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?messageid=%3C3c8770e1%40news%2Ecapgemini%2Ese%3E' title='Re: Netscape 4.7 udfordring - &lt;table width&gt; ...'>Re: Netscape 4.7 udfordring - &lt;table width&gt; ...</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(07-03-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;Claus&nbsp;Rasmussen)</small></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><div class='newsbox'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_reply.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign/default.asp?mode=form&amp;ReplyID=%3C3c8752e